quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  36,13,"Piyan-…ďe yeru, fii yim…ďe saare, tuma nde Nulaa…ďe ngarunoo …ďe,"
  36,14,"Nde Min nulunoo e ma…ď…ďe, [Nulaa…ďe] …ói…óo, …ďe njeddii i …ďen, Min cammbiniri …ďen, tata…ďo, …ďe mbi'i: "Minen, ko men Nulaa…ďe e mo'on"."
  36,15,"[Yim…ďe saare nden] wi'i: "On ngonaani, si wanaa ko on …ďanndiŇčke wano menen. Jom-hinaranke On jippinaani hay hu'unde, on wonaani, si wanaa ko on fenoo…ďe"."
  36,16,"[Nulaa…ďe …ďen] mbi'i: "Joomi amen no anndi pellet, ko min Nulaa…ďe e mo'on."
  36,17,"Fawaaki men non, si wonaa jottingol …ďanngina"."
  36,18,"[Yim…ďe saare nden] mbi'iti: "Min kiitori on kataa. Si tawii non on ka…óitaaki, ma min pi…óu on, lepte mu'usuu…óe kadi memira on immorde e amen"."
  36,19,"[Nulaa…ďe …ďen kadi] mb'iti: "Kiite mon …óin, hi…óon ngon'di e mum. Ko si on mbaajaama (kiitino…óon)? Tigi on, ko on yim…ďe fantinoo…ďe!"."
  36,20,"Gorko iwri ka …ďuri wo…ó…óude e saare nden, o ari homo yaccoo, o wi'i: "eey mon yo yim…ďe am, kori njokkee Nulaa…ďe …ďen,"
  36,21,"Njokkee …ďen …ďe la…ďndotaako on njo…ďdi, …ďen ko feewnaa…ďe."
  36,22,"E ko ha…óata kam rewugol On tak…óo Kam? Ko ka makko woni ruttorde mon."
  36,23,"E mi jogtoto dewetee…ói ga makko? Si Jom-yurmeende On muuyanii kam lorra, tefoore majji duncantaali kam hay hu'unde, …ói nda…óandataa kam kadi."
  36,24,"Haray miin on tuma, mi wonii e majjere …ďanngunde."
  36,25,"Min on, mi gooŇč…óinii Joomi mon, nananee kam"."
  36,26,"[O] wi'anaa: "Naatu Aljanna". O wi'i: "Haaniino yim…ďe am …ďen ngannda,"
  36,27,"ko Joomi am haforani kam, O wa…ói kam e teddinaa…ďe …ďeen"."